{"arkId":"cl010113231","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113231","modified ":"2025-08-28","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1756 - 1759","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 13","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1756,"endYear":1759,"imprecision":"","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Ducrollay, Jean-Charles","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1712","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"avant 1766","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12148","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; tabati\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re en or cisel\u00e9e de deux couleurs, mont\u00e9e \u00e0 cage avec six plaques de porcelaine. D\u00e9cor produit par la Manufacture de S\u00e8vres. Tabati\u00e8re dite \u0022\u00e0 femme\u0022 par ses dimensions r\u00e9duites et sa th\u00e9matique f\u00e9minine. Nouveau type de d\u00e9cor en vogue au milieu du XVIII\u00e8me si\u00e8cle. La manufacture de S\u00e8vres a entrepris de commercialiser de petites plaques \u00e0 fonds color\u00e9s et \u00e0 d\u00e9cors d\u0027amours qui t\u00e9moignent des innovations des peintres au m\u00eame titre que les grands panneaux de porcelaine compos\u00e9s pour le d\u00e9cor des meubles. \r\nAinsi les plaques de cette tabati\u00e8re portent-elles le nouveau fond vert mis au point \u00e0 S\u00e8vres et inaugur\u00e9 avec le nouveau service du Roi livr\u00e9 en 1756.\r\nTabati\u00e8re appel\u00e9e \u0022vert enfants\u0022","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,1","displayDimension":"3,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"5,9","displayDimension":"5,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : porcelaine\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Vente par Lazare Duvaux, 22 octobre 1757 ; collection Louis-Marie-Bretagne-Dominique de Rohan Chabot, duc de Rohan (1710-1791) ; vente, Paris, h\u00f4tel Drouot, salle 3, 17 d\u00e9cembre 1984, n\u00b0 105 ; collection priv\u00e9e, Pays-Bas jusqu\u0027en 2001 ; acquis par John Whitehead Works of Art, 2002 ; acquis, 2004","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"08\/04\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"14\/04\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"15\/04\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partemen